name: El Nido Family Centers
review_text:
This is the Slauson location.
Very cool center in the community, for families in need.
They have a TON of resources!! And the nice pretty lady Lisa Jackson is very knowledgeable about the goins-on with all the programs there and she loves her job!! Carla is very sweet too. Most of the employees there are kind

I love this place❤️
Thank you El Nido, for existing and helping our communities 👍🏾

review_text: En esta ocasión visite está institución para que me hicieran mi declaración de impuestos. Felicitaciones por su gran labor en pro de la comunidad.
